<%= h3_with_anchor "Optimization Tips" %>

<ol>
    <li><strong>Use Specific Queries:</strong> More specific terms = faster searches</li>
    <li><strong>Limit Results:</strong> Only request as many files as needed</li>
    <li><strong>Batch Searches:</strong> Use parallel execution for multiple queries</li>
    <li><strong>Path Filters:</strong> Combine path and content for narrower search</li>
    <li><strong>Index Maintenance:</strong> Regular VACUUM and ANALYZE operations</li>
</ol>

